"Falling Into Infinity" (1997)  
  Lines In The Sand  
  
  *This is most of "Lines in the Sand." It's not perfect, and it's not*  
  *all the way complete, but it's here, and it's okay.*  
  *Side note that no one will care about, but I feel I must tell the*  
  *most people I can, I actually got to meet Mr. Petrucci, along with*  
  *Mr. LaBrie, Mr. Sherinian, and Mr. Portnoy at the recent (5/20/98)*  
  *concert in Tempe, Arizona. What a treat. They were probably the*  
  *most engaging bunch of rock stars I'll ever hope to meet, which is*  
  *just fine because they could just about be the be all end all of*  
  *progressive metal, in my book.*  
  *Can't wait for the new album, guys, if you happen to read this.*  
