  Honor Thy Father  
  
  *Notes: I just got the cd, and it's heavier than everything else out there.*  
  *I'm sure John Petrucci uses a 7 string for most of the album. Anyway, here's*  
  *my tab for the song "Honor Thy Father", it's in Dropped D tuning one full*  
  *step down (C G C F A D), and played with a lot of distortion. I only figured*  
  *out about half the song so far, the rest will come as soon as my fingers*  
  *stop bleeding. For those who don't know where the "verse" or "chorus" is, I*  
