Erotomania  
  
  *I started work on this a few days ago. Since then I hear it's*  
  *been transcribed by Guitar World and some British magazine. I don't*  
  *have enough spare time to sweat out stuff that's already been published,*  
  *so here's what I got done - the first four minutes. It's one hell of*  
  *a tune!*  
  *Oh yeah, I also forgot about Petrucci's 7-string axe. Thus your mileage*  
  *may vary here.*  
  
  *Key:*  
